{"tid":442022,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重複排隊搶購墨爾本超市奶粉　澳洲女子當面斥「你們合法但是錯的」","createTime":"2017-10-20T08:27:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-20T11:38:59.000Z","uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f152a490737c51c1ae78507e03277f273a4b3cd5","tid":442022,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:27:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/international/%E9%87%8D%E8%A4%87%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A%E6%90%B6%E8%B3%BC%E5%A2%A8%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%AC%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E7%95%B6%E9%9D%A2%E6%96%A5-%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E9%8C%AF%E7%9A%84/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A4%2587%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%2590%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E7%25B2%2589-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2580%2591%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%258C%25AF%25E7%259A%2584%2F&d=A7kOZpoo0mE6aRkvZ0BVTYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=aee26fe1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Finternational%2F%25E9%2587%258D%25E8%25A4%2587%25E6%258E%2592%25E9%259A%258A%25E6%2590%25B6%25E8%25B3%25BC%25E5%25A2%25A8%25E7%2588%25BE%25E6%259C%25AC%25E8%25B6%2585%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E7%25B2%2589-%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E6%25B4%25B2%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%25AD%2590%25E7%2595%25B6%25E9%259D%25A2%25E6%2596%25A5-%25E4%25BD%25A0%25E5%2580%2591%25E5%2590%2588%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%2598%25AF%25E9%258C%25AF%25E7%259A%2584%2F&h=31e2a36a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/international/%E9%87%8D%E8%A4%87%E6%8E%92%E9%9A%8A%E6%90%B6%E8%B3%BC%E5%A2%A8%E7%88%BE%E6%9C%AC%E8%B6%85%E5%B8%82%E5%A5%B6%E7%B2%89-%E6%BE%B3%E6%B4%B2%E5%A5%B3%E5%AD%90%E7%95%B6%E9%9D%A2%E6%96%A5-%E4%BD%A0%E5%80%91%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E4%BD%86%E6%98%AF%E9%8C%AF%E7%9A%84/</a><br />\n<br />\n一名澳洲人前日（18日）在澳洲連鎖超市 Coles 的 facebook專頁上載一段短片，顯示有十數名亞洲人面孔的顧客在一間超級市場內搶購奶粉。該名網民描述這些顧客重複地去收銀處付錢然後再回來購買奶粉，指有關行為雖然合法，卻十分荒謬，認為超市應該有政策限制顧客在特定時間內能夠購買多少奶粉。<br />\n<br />\n上載短片的網民 Hannah Dixon 指，片段在澳洲墨爾本的一間超級市場內拍攝。片段顯示，有十數名亞洲面孔的顧客在奶粉還未有上架前，就從運載貨物的手推車上將奶粉放到自己的購物籃裡，平均每人拿走4-6罐奶粉。<br />\n<br />\n一名亞洲面孔男子上前嘗試阻止拍攝，並以英語說「你不能拍攝，這是私隱，你沒有我的批准，你為什麼要拍我」。相信是拍攝短片的女子以英語回應指：「這是可以的，你可以買這些奶粉」，她續指「不過他們在重複地做這件事，他們去收銀處付錢後又再回來。」她又表示，「你們是在欺騙這個系統，」「我知道這是合法的，但這仍然是錯的。」<br />\n<br />\n有人說普通話<br />\n<br />\n片段中亦顯示有人用普通話說：「不要擠」。一名排隊購買奶粉的亞洲女子用英語反問：「（如果是錯的）為什麼他們還在賣？難道他們違規了嗎？錯在哪兒了？」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nHannah Dixon澳洲媒體 A Current Affair 訪問時形容，這班亞洲顧客當時在超市內走來走去，形容當時的情況「瘋狂」，並猜測這班亞洲顧客之間互相合作。<br />\n<br />\nColes 回應澳洲媒體 The Australian 查詢時表示，超市已經有政策限制每名顧客只能購買四罐奶粉。<br />\n<br />\n有香港網民在片段下留言表示，這情況就猶如在香港。<br />\n<br />\n在香港，行政長官林鄭月娥在上星期公佈的任內首份《施政報告》中提出檢討「限奶令」，引起社會討論，有市民擔心如果取消「限奶令」會導致走水貨奶粉的問題變得更加嚴重。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WJj4S2usikc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWJj4S2usikc&d=A7kOZpoo0mE6aRkvZ0BVTYzZXVCnaYNE8CBFJ%2F%2FgXXY%3D&h=47d2867f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=WJj4S2usikc</a>"},{"pid":"525060491d987c66191c7b2920b6987dae04e122","tid":442022,"uid":11962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:30:38.000Z","msg":"支那人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不意外"},{"pid":"f9a2df7660773c0e98a154ab031063934ef5613e","tid":442022,"uid":91721,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:40:41.000Z","msg":"支那人三之黃禍再臨"},{"pid":"8da344cd3ab32df59e7f40f4546522339d9de8ce","tid":442022,"uid":41116,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:42:11.000Z","msg":"道德呢d 野支那人識鬼"},{"pid":"0db9f41ebbe510eba5cde9cbe77b65dee5c36a0d","tid":442022,"uid":118120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:43:46.000Z","msg":"典型中國人思想<br />\n<br />\n因為走灰色地帶, 唔犯法所以就佔盡便宜<br />\n<br />\n買人地d 衫去宴會, 著完就退款, 人地知你地d 貪便宜行為好耐"},{"pid":"593ab6f9e77a12ece2e597918731234c60856d08","tid":442022,"uid":13257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T08:47:43.000Z","msg":"同中國人講呢d哂9氣"},{"pid":"56410a8417ddcb7b30e7e5272f10f73d3264ffba","tid":442022,"uid":67338,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:19:01.000Z","msg":"傑出華人系列"},{"pid":"c3da60ab253cfe8819643fe47ea3d5dd7a5b7e49","tid":442022,"uid":60366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:26:22.000Z","msg":"亞洲面孔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全澳洲都知係得中國人會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDaigou依個term個個都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d485456dae8a09e8f0d9398b1120ee39ee7ad9e5","tid":442022,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-20T11:38:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>亞洲面孔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n根本全澳洲都知係得中國人會咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nDaigou依個term個個都知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n除咗支那人仲有邊個要搶奶粉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}